---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About 1H Crypto" lang="en">

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">About 1H Crypto</h1>
  <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-8">An independent trader doing BTC & ETH intraday analysis using the Al Brooks price action methodology.</p>
  <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--text-secondary)] text-sm leading-relaxed">
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Not An Analyst</h3><p>I am an independent trader who uses Al Brooks price action analysis for crypto intraday analysis. No investment advice, no signal calls, no private groups.</p></div>
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Research Framework</h3><p>Every day at 08:00 Beijing Time (00:00 UTC), I publish a BTC/USDT and ETH/USDT hourly price action analysis covering candlestick patterns, on-chain data, derivatives sentiment, and paper trading results.</p></div>
    <div class="card p-6"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">The Goal</h3><p>365 days, 365 verified price action analysis records. A research archive no one can replicate.</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
